Name: Log Service Message Registry
Description: This registry defines the messages for log service related events.

DiagnosticDataCollected.Description: Indicates that diagnostic data was collected due to a client invoking the `CollectDiagnosticData` action.
DiagnosticDataCollected.LongDescription: This message shall indicate that diagnostic data was collected due to a client invoking the `CollectDiagnosticData` action.
ArgLongDescriptions: This argument shall contain the value of the `DiagnosticDataType` parameter provided by the client when the `CollectDiagnosticData` action was invoked.
